  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "PORTFOLIO MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Overview:</strong></p><p>We are seeking experienced discretionary proprietary traders specializing in foreign exchange (FX). The ideal candidate will have a proven and profitable trading track record, strong risk management discipline, and at\nleast three years of relevant trading experience.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>- Trade major and minor FX pairs using discretionary strategies.</p><p>- Manage risk prudently within predefined parameters.</p><p>- Conduct market analysis and identify high-probability trading opportunities.</p><p>- Maintain and improve trading performance through disciplined execution and continuous strategy refinement.</p><p>- Collaborate with the team on market insights and trading ideas.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>- Minimum 3 years of experience trading FX in a discretionary capacity.</p><p>- Demonstrated and verifiable record of consistent profitability.</p><p>- Deep understanding of FX markets, macroeconomic factors, and technical analysis.</p><p>- Strong risk management skills and emotional discipline under pressure.</p><p>- Self-motivated, detail-oriented, and capable of independent decision-making.</p><p><strong>Preferred:</strong></p><p>- Experience trading with hedge fund, family office, proprietary capital or at a prop firm.</p>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 3,
